      • createComponentUI

        <T extends Configuration> ComponentAddonUI<? extends T> createComponentUI(T configuration)
                                                                   throws AddonException,
                                                                          ConfigurationException
        Creates an component addon user interface compatible with the configuration, and initializes it with the configuration.
        Parameters:
        configuration - Configuration to edit.
        Returns:
        The created component addon UI, initialized with the given configuration.
        Throws:
        AddonException - Thrown if no factory for the given component type exists, or if the addon does not create configurations of the given configuration class.
        ConfigurationException - Thrown if corresponding component addon was found, but configuration was invalid.
